    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s still in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it feels and smells brand new! It drives like an absolute dream and there isn't a single mark on it. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, quick sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move fast. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love for this to go to a great home! \u2728",
