      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out. I've pampered this car since day one, and it still has that 'new car' feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Swing by and take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
