    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically flawless example featuring the S55 3.0L twin-mono-scroll turbocharged inline-six mated to a crisp 7-speed M-DCT. This vehicle boasts a rigid chassis with an Adaptive M Suspension system that remains in factory-spec calibration. The drivetrain is anchored by an electronically controlled Active M Differential, providing exceptional lateral dynamics. Equipped with carbon-ceramic brakes for superior thermal management and reduced unsprung mass, the car exhibits zero fluid seepage and a pristine undercarriage. Every bushing, seal, and actuator functions with surgical precision.",
